<P>
   &UR; BAN DIVX  &LR; _ Divx, a pay-per-view digital video format that
rivals the new DVD, is barely out yet, but already it's provoking
controversy, with a grassroots `Ban Divx' campaign. And heavyweight
companies like Warner Home Video, Tower, Fryes, Sam Goody also
oppose it. By Dan Fost
