   THREE BOXES: cable vs. netowork ratings for kid viewing; comedy
choices on Wed nite (pretty much nothing but South Park on Comedy
Ctrl); and a few shows the networks are hoping will be hits come
fall. (Holloway, Austin American-Statesman).
</P>
