central bank acts to protect the ruble amid calls for a
devaluation; Moody's downgrades its rating on Russian debt. By
Michel Wines. With: MOSCOW-ASSESS and RUSSIA-MARKETPLACE.
</P>
<P>
   WASHINGTON
</P>
