<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1998-08-13 17:03 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A2596 &Cx1f; taf-z
u e &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-GIRL-THEATER-REVIEW-N     08-13 0760
