<P>
   &UR; INTERNATIONAL (i) &LR;
</P>
<P>
   EMBASSY-BODIES (Andrews Air Force Base, Md.) _ The remains of 10
Americans killed in the Nairobi embassy bombing are returned to the
United States. By Estella Duran. 1200 words.
</P>
<P>
   w/
</P>
<P>
   &UR; WASHINGTON (w) &LR;
</P>
<P>
   CLINTON-ADVISERS (Washington) -- With the president preparing to
