BBN-BRAVES (Los Angeles) _ Feature on the Atlanta Braves. The
Braves have ruled the National League the past few seasons but have
come up woefully short in the postseason. Their Achilles' heel, the
bullpen, is again making them an iffy proposition for the World
Series. &QL; 
By Eric Noland. (Will move on the ``s'' sports file.)
