SOUTHPAW CELEBS 
</HEADLINE>
   (For use by N.Y. Times News Service clients)  
 c.1998 The Arizona Republic  
<TEXT>
<P>
   UNDATED - If you're a lefty and have ever experienced times of
isolation or the awkwardness of living in a right-handed world,
relax. The company you share just happens to be the cream of the
backward crop _ with a few exceptions.
</P>
<P>
   Actors: Jason Alexander, Tim Allen, Fred Astaire, Dan Aykroyd,
Matthew Broderick, Jim Carrey, Charlie Chaplin, Tom Cruise, Robert
De Niro, Matt Dillon, David Duchovny, W.C. Fields, Laurence
