<DATE_TIME> 1998-08-13 22:16 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A3170 &Cx1f; taf-z
u a &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-NY-SENATE-ASSESS-NYT &LR;      08-13 0962
